text: "Cherry Wine" is a 2012 song by American rapper Nas. Cherry Wine may also refer to: *Cherry wine, a type of fruit wine made with cherries *"Cherry Wine" (Hozier song), a 2016 song by Hozier *"Cherry Wine" (Little Esther song), a 1953 song by Little Esther * Cherry Wine (horse), second finisher in the 2016 Preakness Stakes ==See also== * "Sweet Cherry Wine", a 1969 song by Tommy James and the Shondells
title: Cherry Wine (disambiguation)
